{"tid":1461203,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有冇人去左九龍俾支持被捕義士","createTime":"2019-08-13T06:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T07:22:46.000Z","uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6551c38a86576329ec49cd4741252403d9bd08e4","tid":1461203,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:40:45.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】星期日包圍尖沙咀警署事件，十六人涉嫌非法集結，一人涉參與暴動，案件下午提堂。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，星期日晚上七時三十分，一批示威者在尖沙咀警署外聚集，部分示威者向警員投硬物，更有人懷疑向警署投擲汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n警方驅散行動中拘捕30人，當中13男3女，年齡介乎14至27歲，被控一項參與非法集結罪；一名24歲男子被控參與暴動罪，下午在九龍城裁判法院提堂。"},{"pid":"ba09050300447b634aaa6e488daa5ad9063cfe05","tid":1461203,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e428ef4c98f065d5718cfca043681c651e4f30","tid":1461203,"uid":15592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:45:58.000Z","msg":"一人暴動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係任佢charge <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8304e2ac4779deb7668b73c5bb3520a7af11bfb0","tid":1461203,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:55:49.000Z","msg":"好似大家都係focus機場<br />\nSAD"},{"pid":"223067ec20443dc2781ac579f20fd53e6efe5aac","tid":1461203,"uid":181703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8304e2ac4779deb7668b73c5bb3520a7af11bfb0","tid":1461203,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:55:49.000Z","msg":"好似大家都係focus機場<br />\nSAD"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:04:42.000Z","msg":"而家去會否太遲?"},{"pid":"fc7541a43b22fbf92d4a1b986ecb6dc9c207ac16","tid":1461203,"uid":134518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p